product: SOLARA Unbreakable Resistance Band for Exercise (11pc)| 100% Natural Latex Fitness Resistance Tube | Resistance Bands for ...
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
Quality, Warranty, and Good Customer Service, what more can you ask for?
body:
Honest review. This is my take on the product as I see it, since I feel it's worth the buy, apart from sense of security the warranty provides.‚Ä¢ 3 layer packaging : Sturdy Solara box on the outside that keeps all the products on the inside safe from any damage due to shipping.In my case there was slight damage to the outer box but thanks to that everything was perfectly fine on the inside. Well thought out.‚Ä¢ Carry on bag : Ample space on the inside, and big enough that you can easily store the resistance tubes and accessories without cramming it together, unlike another similar product I recently tried.‚Ä¢ Accessories : Solara brand name on everything so you know what you see is what you get.Adjustable ankle straps suitable for any size.Strong door anchor with quality foam on the outside ring.Good handles with enough hand room.‚Ä¢ Connections : Can easily hook all the tubes together in combination to any of the connecting steel links.‚Ä¢ Resistance tubes :Thicker tubes as described.Strong steel hooks/ carabiners.Weight markings on each tube strap.Good resistance even on the Yellow 10lbs/4.5 kg tube.Slightly strong latex smell because of more latex used I guess but the tubes feel much more resistant as a result.Will update on durability after a few months, but if you're worried about that, just give a call to the phone no. given in relation to warranty claims and all that before you buy the product.‚Ä¢ Customer care line : Was very courteous and helpful in choosing this specific product.‚Ä¢ Warranty  : Only someone confident in their product would offer a 2 year warranty plus 6 months ( Vip membership card on the inside that gives you additional 6 months warranty) on top of a 10 day replacement.Overall Much Better Quality compared to the previous product I bought (more than 13,000 reviews but when it came,  was nothing like the images, no weight markings, no brand name on anything except the carry on bag, and low quality tubes that felt like they would snap after a few uses.Hopefully this was helpful as a first review. Feel free to share your own personal experiences with this product.

product: SOLARA Unbreakable Resistance Band for Exercise (11pc)| 100% Natural Latex Fitness Resistance Tube | Resistance Bands for ...
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Performance and customer service
body:
I would rate this product somewhere between 3.5 to 4 stars. This is after using the bands for almost 1 month.Durability of the product- 4 starsThey claim to be unbreakable. But after merely using it 3 times, the yellow band snapped. This can be due to faulty products or fake claims of being unbreakable. But according to me, the reason could be the faulty product (which can happen in any product line). This is because the other bands which have been used much more rigorously have stood the test of unbreakable till now.Customer service- 3.5 starsThis is the most important factor, at least for me. I e-mailed them when my yellow band snapped. The response was not prompt. They asked me the proof of the band which broke. And after providing them with the image of the respective band, they sent me the replacement (which arrived within 3 days). They said in the mail that they would provide me with the details (for tracking) when they would dispatch the shipment, but the said details were not provided and I kept waiting for it (and one fine day I got my replacement).Overall verdictThe bands are durable and stand the test of unbreakability. Customer service could see some improvements. Overall the product is very good if you wish to work out at home.I would update the review regarding its durability, after some more months.

body:
Recently, I've purchased these gym gloves, and I am quite satisfied with my purchase! These gloves have completely transformed my workout experience, and it couldn't be much easier.Firstly, the fit is absolutely perfect. I was concerned about finding gloves that wouldn't be too tight or too loose, but these gloves seem to have been tailor-made for my hands. The snug fit provides excellent support without sacrificing comfort, allowing me to focus entirely on my exercises.The grip these gloves offer is outstanding. Whether I'm lifting weights, using resistance bands, or doing bodyweight exercises, the enhanced grip ensures that I can maintain proper form without worrying about my hands slipping. It's made a noticeable difference in the effectiveness of my workouts.Moreover, the durability of these gloves is impressive. I've put them through some intense sessions, and they still look and feel brand new. The quality of materials used is evident, and it's reassuring to know that my investment will last.What surprised me the most, though, is how breathable these gloves are. I was initially concerned about sweaty hands, but the well-designed ventilation kept my hands cool and dry throughout my entire workout. It's a small detail that makes a big impact on overall comfort.In conclusion, these gym gloves have exceeded my expectations in every way. They've become an essential part of my gym routine, and I can't imagine working out without them. If you're in the market for reliable, comfortable, and high-performance gym gloves, look no further‚Äîthese are the real deal!

product: KORE DM-HEXA-5KG-COMBO16 Dumbbells Kits
title:
5.0 out of 5 stars
A Great Addition to My Home Gym
body:
I recently purchased the KORE DM-HEXA-10KG-COMBO16 Dumbbells Kit, and I can honestly say that this kit has exceeded my expectations and has added a new level of versatility to my home workout regimen.First off, I'd like to commend the quality of the product. The hexagonal design is a huge plus - the dumbbells don't roll off when I put them down, and they remain steady and safe during my workouts. They are also coated with a durable rubber material that provides a good grip, and has so far proven to be resistant to sweat and wear.The weight (10 kg each, 20 kg in total) is substantial enough for both basic workouts and more intensive strength training. What's more, the weight is evenly distributed which helps maintain balance and control during use. These dumbbells have been instrumental in me being able to perform a wide range of exercises that work out different muscle groups.The set arrived in excellent condition, packaged securely to prevent any damage. Also, I appreciate that they were ready to use right out of the box, with no assembly required, which saved me time and hassle.For the price point, I was impressed with the quality and durability of the dumbbells. Compared to other options on the market, the KORE DM-HEXA-10KG-COMBO16 Dumbbells Kit provides excellent value for money.To sum up, these dumbbells are sturdy, reliable, and perfect for home workouts. They've allowed me to diversify my training and reach new fitness goals. I highly recommend them to anyone who's looking to invest in high-quality home gym equipment.

This shorts length is just correct - way above the knees, tight at the thighs and buttocks and gives a very sexy feeling wearing it.Wow, what a product- even now as I am typing this, my male organ is getting hard inside. product: BodyFit B-30 Kg Weight Plates Rods Leather Gym Gloves Set Dumbbell Exercise Set (multicolour, 1 X 5ft, 1 X 3ft, 2 X 14-Inch)
title:
4.0 out of 5 stars
Value for money product.
body:
All items mentioned have been provided. All weights are delivered without any damage.I have a small problem with the Z shaped bar. The place where we add weights is not straight and the weight wobbles a bit.Apart from that I don't have any issues and I recommend this product.The circular hole in the weight disks are bigger and the rod provided is small.(especially the Z bar). So weight disks will be loose and rotating even though clips are attached. A nice trick is to use insulation tape to wind the rod to make it thick where the weight disks are attached to the rod. This makes the weight disks stay stable and straight.
Read more

product: BodyFit B-30 Kg Weight Plates Rods Leather Gym Gloves Set Dumbbell Exercise Set (multicolour, 1 X 5ft, 1 X 3ft, 2 X 14-Inch)
title:
3.0 out of 5 stars
Excellent package for the given price.
body:
Bought them a week ago. Have posted a few images of the same. The package delivered had all the contents as mentioned.Positives:1. The rods are good; some said that they were a bit thin but I found them to be nice for workout.2. The dumbells are very nice. Its locks too are good.3. The weights are compact and fine enough for the price.4. Wrist bands and gloves are also good.5. The sack is really cool.Negatives:1. A couple of weights came dented. It was a bit disappointing to see that.2. The clips for rod are not tight enough. There is a slight clearance which is a bit annoying.3. The skipping rope came broken.Verdict:For Rs. 1600/- this is a very nice product. Since my aim is to reduce weight and try basic exercises, they are enough for me. If you have a budget constraint, do consider it.
